Package request

Class RegisterMemberRequest

java.lang.Object
request.RegisterMemberRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RegisterMemberRequest extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a request to register a new subscriber (member) in the system. This request is sent from the client to the server (via OCSF), and contains all personal and vehicle information required to create a new subscriber entry in the database.
